sentences.english: The heroic deeds of the people's soldiers are too numerous to enumerate.
sentences.chinese: 人民子弟兵的事蹟舉不勝舉。

sentences.english: Examples are too many to cite.
There are numerous reasons why women may lose interest in sex.
sentences.chinese: 女人對性失去興趣的原因有很多，舉不勝舉。

sentences.english: In a wide range of basic infrastructure, the examples are too many to name here.
sentences.chinese: 就廣泛的基礎設施而言，相關的例證更是舉不勝舉。

sentences.english: Examples are too numerous to list.
It would be an endless task to cite such living examples.
